&lt;p&gt;Portsmouth Community Stroke Rehabilitation Team has a vacancy for a band 5 nurse .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working across the Portsmouth, Gosport and Petersfield areas, supported by other senior staff and an interdisciplinary team to provide patient focused stroke rehabilitation in patients&#39; own homes. There is  a direct patient focus with responsibility for patient transfers into and out of the team and co-ordination of visits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be a competent car driver, with access to a car for work purposes, and be able to problem solve, as you will be working alone and in complex situations.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are an experienced nurse and you wish to work in a locally and nationally recognised specialist stroke team – pleased contact us! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date 18/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
